org.apache.hadoop.resourceestimator.common.api

Class RecurrenceId

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.resourceestimator.common.api.RecurrenceId

  • public class RecurrenceId
extends Object
    RecurrenceId is the id for the recurring pipeline jobs.

    We assume that the pipeline job can be uniquely identified with {pipelineId, runId}.
